{"tid":641642,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲有唔要既黃子華棟篤笑飛可以俾我","createTime":"2018-04-25T07:14:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T09:50:14.000Z","uid":37733,"like":3,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3e715e9266aa4ebad7a4f9fb2a3e1bd33db9d30d","tid":641642,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T07:14:03.000Z","msg":"利申左先 屋企冇乜錢買飛<br />\n唔係話窮到穿窿 但就算有多餘錢都唔係去買飛<br />\n<br />\n我黎緊想去睇棟篤笑 買張飛幾百蚊好似唔太貴 <br />\n但屋企唔太多錢 幾百蚊食到一個星期了 <br />\n<br />\n所以睇下有冇巴絲有d連座位唔連位ge二手飛讓出黎 <br />\n送比我就當然最好 但如果係平平地放比我我都唔介意嫁 <br />\n希望各位巴絲幫幫忙 如果有野想交換可以問下我 <br />\n<br />\n祝各位新年快樂  新年願望除左香港建國 共匪倒台之外 <br />\n其中一個細細地ge願望就係想自己有個睇到黃子華棟篤笑ge飛 等自己生活冇咁頹廢"},{"pid":"474317656c0e32c161f792236bf45013f051ea45","tid":641642,"uid":146861,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T07:16:02.000Z","msg":"假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d86b0987bee415e1e95ae4950d80cc1aeca3a4c3","tid":641642,"uid":31254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T07:16:28.000Z","msg":"pmed"},{"pid":"9258b030d927fee100e5696270fa17f0a5cfb657","tid":641642,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T07:16:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心求飛"},{"pid":"930c6f1e1b985fc4badac076cf4ceb3af06e41fc","tid":641642,"uid":166792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T07:18:23.000Z","msg":"好似有 <br />\n唔黐線 唔正常 <br />\n要既PM"},{"pid":"40b666fef12080777b97afbf6bda13cf9d05e4a5","tid":641642,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T07:20:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似有 <br />\n唔黐線 唔正常 <br />\n要既PM</blockquote><br />\n想睇金盤浪口"},{"pid":"26e5247dc9f2d7643213a988c09f2141e8926900","tid":641642,"uid":74207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9258b030d927fee100e5696270fa17f0a5cfb657","tid":641642,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,